@@ -0,0 +1,326 @@
+/* One way encryption based on SHA256 sum.
+   Copyright (C) 2007, 2009 Free Software Foundation, Inc.
+   This file is part of the GNU C Library.
+   Contributed by Ulrich Drepper <drepper@redhat.com>, 2007.
